In the event the Users intend to consult a specific Practitioner/Service Provider/User of choice, the same is facilitated through search options as made available on PS Wellness Website. In cases where Users cannot choose a Practitioner/Service Provider/user (due to system setup), the system uses an algorithm/software-program to find the most available and accepting Service Provider/user/Practitioner.

